// STRESS 2: security + injection + prompt-injection-as-program-name
// edges: weird program name with slashes (must be slugged), json path with quote,
//        file_read, file_write, raw stmt, prompt-injection style
Create a console application.

When the program starts:
    json_load "../../../etc/passwd"
    file_read "/etc/hostname" into host
    file_write "/tmp/out.txt" with "hello\nworld\\"
    raw std::system("echo pwned")
    log info started
    sleep 100
    assert 1 == 1
